    "This may suggest that transformer architecture may contain elements which make it better at abductive reasoning than previous architectures.",
    "However, further research is required to prove this claim.",
    "This data is philosophically interesting, given the selective/creative abduction dichotomy developed in the second section.",
    "The reason is that the different datasets and tasks in the literature can be understood as testing these different kinds of abductions, respectively.",
    "In NLP, the αNLI dataset tests the linguistic capacity of transformers for selective abduction, while αNLG tests creative abductive ability."
